cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

Reasoning: 
1) cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a vehicle tracking method based on image sensors and convolutional neural networks. 
2) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses a human attention mechanism for self-selection of deep features. 
3) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a two-stage method for model training. 
4) cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper discusses the application of the proposed method in intelligent transportation systems. 
5) cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with image and video processing for vehicle tracking.
